                "title": "Cicin Sarkıtı"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Element Becerisi</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">1 </span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Buz Hasarı </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">verir ve </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\">Buz Cicinler </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">çağırır.</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/28/145542732/1a979041a9881649ba69332b20dd5820_389443932318479954.png",
                "id": "talent61895",
                "key": "Sislerin İçinden",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "cryo"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Sislerin İçinden"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Element Patlaması</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">5 </span><span style=\"color: #99FFFF\">Buz Hasarı </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">verir ve bu karaktere </span><span style=\"color: #99FFFF\">Buz Etkisi </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">kazandırarak 1 </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\">Sarmalayan Cicin Kalkanı </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">oluşturur.</span></p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\">Sarmalayan Cicin Kalkanı</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Savaş Durumu</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">Aktif karakterin için 1 </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\">Kalkan puanı </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">sağlar. Oluşturulduğunda alanda </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\">Buz Cicinler </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">varsa </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\">Kalkan</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">, sahip olduğu </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\">Kullanım Hakkı </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">kadar artar. (En fazla 3 </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\">Kalkan </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">ekler.)</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/28/145542732/8d60085e1f79ee9a2bb87006d7f2d32c_8108211724648546199.png",
                "id": "talent1338",
                "key": "Karlı Dallarda Açan Çiçekler",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "cryo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Karlı Dallarda Açan Çiçekler"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Minyon</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\">Son Aşama: </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">1 </span><span style=\"color: #99FFFF\">Buz Hasarı </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">verir.</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\">Kullanım Hakkı: </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">2 (En fazla 3 kademe birikebilir.)</span></p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\">Fatui Buz Cicin Büyücüsü bir Normal Saldırı yaptıktan sonra </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">bu kart 1 </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\">Kullanım Hakkı</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\"> kazanır.</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\">Karakterin Element Tepkimesi Hasarı aldıktan sonra</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\"> bu kart 1 </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\">Kullanım Hakkı </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">kaybeder.</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/28/145542732/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_675144921881692837.png",
                "id": "talent87506",
                "key": "Minyon - Buz Cicinler",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/28/145542732/1467dd7dd3fec80047e77cc996621508_7799515461265099011.png",
                "title": "Minyon - Buz Cicinler"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">Buz Etkisi uygular ve şu Element Tepkimelerini tetikleyebilir: <br>[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Buz </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">+ </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Ateş</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">] </span><strong><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\">Erime: </span></strong><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">Bu seferki Hasar 2 artar.</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Buz </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">+ </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Elektrik</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">] </span><strong><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\">Süper İletim: </span></strong><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">Bu seferki Hasar 1 artar ve hedef dışındaki tüm rakip karakterlere 1 Delme Hasarı verir.</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Buz </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">+ </span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Su</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">] </span><strong><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\">Donma: </span></strong><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">Bu seferki Hasar 1 artar ve hedef bu turda hamle yapamaz. (Hedef, Fiziksel Hasar ve Ateş Hasarı alınca kaldırılır, fazladan 2 Hasar alır.)</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/28/145542732/4bcc4b82a9d7ee22770f60afa54e9919_556295790779419367.png",
                "id": "talent77135",
                "key": "Buz Hasarı",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Buz Hasarı"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\">Kullanım Hakkı</span></strong><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\"> </span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">Bu kartın etkisi tetiklendikten sonra 1 </span><strong><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">Kullanım Hakkı</span></strong><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\"> harcanır. </span><strong><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">Kullanım Hakkı</span></strong><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\"> 0 olduktan sonra bu kart hemen atılır.</span></p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\">Kalkan</span></strong><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\"> </span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">Bu Kalkan, onu kuşanan karakteri Hasardan korumak için harcanır.</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/28/145542732/245c229cf6f7364c7c9a7aea3db1a1ad_454987257045653175.png",
